		<section>
			<h2>preparation</h2>

			<ol>
			    <li>Run the tap a little so the water's nicely aerated</li>
			    <li>Pop a tea bag</li>
			    <li>Pour the hot water over the tea bag</li>
			    <li>Tea needs time</li>
			    <li>Gently squish the tea bag with a spoon</li>
			    <li>If you want throw it some milk</li>
			    <li>Enjoy!</li>
			</ol>
